<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Ulm</head><p>Der Rat übersendet in Abschrift Neuigkeiten über König Sigismund und die Geschehnisse in Böhmen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_351" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_351_r1l1">Den von Vlme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_351_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / wır tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wiſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ neẅlıchen einem bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l3">vns ein ſchrıft <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> ıſt von gelegenheıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l4">~ des <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc künıgs vnd auch von den lewffen ʒu Beheım </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l5">Dıeſelb ſchrıft vns auf heẅt ıſt fürbracht / Alſo <expan>ſchıke<ex>n</ex></expan> wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l6"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> / <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ſchrıft / ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>verſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ın <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l7"><expan>freẅntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_351_r1l8"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_351" id="174v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von Ulme</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        newlichen einem bey uns ein schrift <expan>kom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> ist von
                        gelegenheit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedigiste<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künigs und auch von den lewffen zu Beheim, dieselb schrift uns auf hewt ist
                        fürbracht; also <expan>schike<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan> schrift ein
                            <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
